    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the pan with your <strong>curry powder</strong> and<strong> </strong>the<strong> rinsed red lentils</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> chopped pepper </strong>and<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong> with a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1674830660271-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1674830660271-x400.jpg",
