      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> trimmed green beans</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil </strong>(or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the green beans to form a tightly sealed parcel[s] and add to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 10-12 min or until the green beans are tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 7,
